Further information about the processing of Personal Data
Children use of Touchgrind Scooter
Touchgrind Scooter is intended for use by general audiences, and we do not knowingly collect or use any Personal Data from children under the age of 13.
Touchgrind Scooter does not demand Users to register so that no personally identifiable information (such as name, surname, email address) is ever collected. However, we may collect non-personally identifiable information such as Usage Data. Other non-personally identifiable information, such as a device ID or any other persistent or temporary identifier, may be collected by third party service providers (advertising and analytics services).
Therefore, the Data collected will not be tied to any personal identifiable information and will be used solely for internal purposes, and precisely: service improvement, security, content personalisation (level updates and in-game rewards accrued) and advertising (non-behavioural).
If you are a parent or a legal guardian of a child between the age of 14 and 17 and you believe that your child is using Touchgrind Scooter, please contact us at support@illusionlabs.se for further information and we will either make sure that we collect your prior consent on behalf of the child or, if you so request, we will delete the information from our system.
If you are a parent or a legal guardian of a child of 13 or under the age of 13 and you believe that your child is using Touchgrind Scooter, please contact us at support@illusionlabs.se and, if you so request, we will delete the information from our system. In any case, although Touchgrind Scooter does not contain any violent, sexual, explicit content whatsoever, we strongly recommend the parent or legal guardian to supervise the use of Touchgrind Scooter by the child.
Touchgrind Scooter is free to download but permits in game-purchases. All the commercial transactions are handled via the iTunes/Apple Store account of the User. This means that we do not collect nor store any credit card data. If you are a parent or a legal guardian that is concerned about this specific feature, you may disable the in-game purchase feature from within your device or by editing your iTunes/Apple Store account settings.
For any further information, User is welcome to contact the Owner at the following email address: support@illusionlabs.se
The Service is not directed to children under the age of 13
Users declare themselves to be adult according to their applicable legislation. Minors may use this Application only with the assistance of a parent or guardian. Under no circumstance persons under the age of 13 may use this Application.
